//   - an object { Type:"annotation", Renderer:Function }: rendered (via
//     "safelyRendered") on the same side and with the same width limits
//     as the last preceding "user"/"assistant" message, but may be
//     arbitrarily tall - useful e.g. for tool calls, citations or other
//     in-between content that is neither a user nor an assistant message
