// marked-plaintext (npm v0.0.2) is incompatible with marked v17 — plain text
// rendering is implemented directly below using the marked v17 renderer API
// see https://marked.js.org/using_pro#renderer
//
// "marked" and its companions are lazily loaded on first use (see
